{"id":302238,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/07/维权网-生存环境遭污染广西藤县村民忍无可忍砸/","date":"2013-07-04T15:17:42Z","modified":"2013-07-04T15:17:42Z","title":"维权网 | 生存环境遭污染广西藤县村民忍无可忍砸烂非法稀土采矿场（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"><span></span><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a>（维权网信息员李军报道）<span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日，广西藤县新庆镇高田村大量村民持锄头、棍棒等武器将村内的非法稀土采矿场砸烂烧毁，随后又前往新庆镇镇政府，将政府门窗砸烂，藤县政府出动大批警察到场镇压。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span><br /><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">  </span><span>藤县当地的稀土非法开采好几年了，致使村民饮水受到严重污染，大量农田及农作物受损，当地人民的生存权受到巨大侵害吧，而当地政府却无所作为，村民长期维权无果，并遭到稀土公司所雇打手殴打。由此引发此次当地人民的激烈抗争。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-tZViY0pygZA/UdVDdjxKZZI/AAAAAAAAkr0/d1QqS5ZckN0/s417/1.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"238\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-tZViY0pygZA/UdVDdjxKZZI/AAAAAAAAkr0/d1QqS5ZckN0/s320/1.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-EBDOX_h18M8/UdVDfHE745I/AAAAAAAAkr8/vub0zU4OYG0/s441/2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"188\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-EBDOX_h18M8/UdVDfHE745I/AAAAAAAAkr8/vub0zU4OYG0/s320/2.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-uqnJTZrCD9g/UdVDfhbpEEI/AAAAAAAAksE/ggGFZL9yjIc/s417/3.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"203\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-uqnJTZrCD9g/UdVDfhbpEEI/AAAAAAAAksE/ggGFZL9yjIc/s320/3.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p> </p></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"